ectra-container has-z-index spectra-sticky-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t<\/div>\n\n\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-d3cf4240-8564-4a0f-8ef6-a059cfb555be\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-z-index: 2\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow wp-block-spectra-container has-z-index\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-266862d3-2b9c-4889-85d3-121e2d03a294\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2)\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6c531013 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\t<h2 data-spectra-id=\"spectra-811b35fa-8f31-4124-8f47-7eef50472c74\" style=\"--spectra-text-color: ast-global-color-5;--spectra-z-index: 3\" class=\"has-text-color has-link-color spectra-text-color wp-elements-f066a2a0ef4b9f77dc96fcbfe31bec8b wp-block-spectra-content has-text-color has-ast-global-color-5-color has-z-index\">\n\t\tIL PESCE\t<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\t<p data-spectra-id=\"spectra-805c30c7-2778-4d9c-a110-0ecc5f371587\" style=\"--spectra-text-color: #ffffff;--spectra-z-index: 3\" class=\"has-text-color spectra-text-color wp-block-spectra-content has-text-color has-ffffff-color has-z-index\">\n\t\tIl pesce che utilizziamo per i nostri piatti \u2014 in particolare <strong>salmone e pesce spada affumicato<\/strong> \u2014 proviene da pesca controllata e certificata. Nel caso del salmone utilizziamo <strong>salmone rosso sockeye selvaggio dell\u2019Alaska<\/strong>, una specie pescata nel Pacifico settentrionale e riconosciuta per la sua qualit\u00e0 e sostenibilit\u00e0. Questo tipo di pesca segue rigorosi sistemi di gestione delle risorse marine, che garantiscono il mantenimento degli ecosistemi e la tutela degli stock ittici.\t<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-9e8e3a6a-16c4-4414-bbc1-f13ddaa6d428\"\tstyle=\"overflow: visible; --spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2);\" class=\"spectra-is-root-container alignfull spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"\t>\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-1553f085-ae9f-4e97-97cf-710a641dc9ae\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2);--spectra-overlay-opacity: 0.1;--spectra-z-index: 1;--spectra-sticky-offset: 0px;--spectra-sticky-keep-inside-parent: 1\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color spectra-dim-ratio wp-block-spectra-container has-z-index spectra-sticky-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t<\/div>\n\n\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-3eeed976-b74e-41db-ae8b-b8081f57c55d\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-z-index: 2\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow wp-block-spectra-container has-z-index\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-4223a7cc-fdab-4007-b11b-8480f2df20de\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2)\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6c531013 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\t<h2 data-spectra-id=\"spectra-d0136557-2090-49e2-9843-9b2637a0a087\" style=\"--spectra-text-color: ast-global-color-5;--spectra-z-index: 3\" class=\"has-text-color has-link-color spectra-text-color wp-elements-0320c2c827d0e90d9556051bbab38ca5 wp-block-spectra-content has-text-color has-ast-global-color-5-color has-z-index\">\n\t\tLE UOVA\t<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\t<p data-spectra-id=\"spectra-d94f331b-c116-42d7-b4b5-53af0d52ef93\" style=\"--spectra-text-color: #ffffff;--spectra-z-index: 3\" class=\"has-text-color spectra-text-color wp-block-spectra-content has-text-color has-ffffff-color has-z-index\">\n\t\tLe uova provengono dall\u2019<strong>allevamento biologico all\u2019aperto della Masseria La Vegliese<\/strong>. Le galline sono allevate in spazi ampi e naturali, dove possono muoversi liberamente e seguire i loro comportamenti naturali. Questo tipo di allevamento garantisce non solo una maggiore attenzione al benessere animale, ma anche una qualit\u00e0 superiore del prodotto finale.\t<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-49222c4b-af4e-4c04-a985-0f95a1a881d6\"\tstyle=\"overflow: visible; --spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2);\" class=\"spectra-is-root-container alignfull spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"\t>\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-330abbfd-7cf6-438c-9f31-dd1d9de21914\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2);--spectra-overlay-opacity: 0.1;--spectra-z-index: 1;--spectra-sticky-offset: 0px;--spectra-sticky-keep-inside-parent: 1\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color spectra-dim-ratio wp-block-spectra-container has-z-index spectra-sticky-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t<\/div>\n\n\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-2de41ae5-b73e-44bb-bdef-23432e0981cc\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-z-index: 2\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow wp-block-spectra-container has-z-index\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-5db4ebbb-eaa8-4848-ab9f-169ca42cc13a\" style=\"overflow: visible;--spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-2)\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6c531013 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\t<h2 data-spectra-id=\"spectra-0d294202-51fc-446b-8a44-2b08170672e1\" style=\"--spectra-text-color: ast-global-color-5;--spectra-z-index: 3\" class=\"has-text-color has-link-color spectra-text-color wp-elements-fd6b961d43580300cd8db0bc1db3ec6d wp-block-spectra-content has-text-color has-ast-global-color-5-color has-z-index\">\n\t\tFRUTTA VERDURA E CEREALI\t<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\t<p data-spectra-id=\"spectra-9734636c-dca2-4afd-9259-a25ca04aa145\" style=\"--spectra-text-color: #ffffff;--spectra-z-index: 3\" class=\"has-text-color spectra-text-color wp-block-spectra-content has-text-color has-ffffff-color has-z-index\">\n\t\tLa nostra cucina utilizza una selezione di <strong>frutta, verdure e cereali provenienti da coltivazioni pugliesi<\/strong>. Anche ingredienti come <strong>avocado, mango o quinoa<\/strong>, che hanno origini tropicali, provengono da produttori locali che li coltivano nel rispetto dei cicli naturali e della terra. Privilegiamo <strong>filiere corte, agricoltura responsabile e fornitori che rispettano il lavoro umano e l\u2019ambiente<\/strong>.\t<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-mhjpwrgs-6jcc85\"\tstyle=\"overflow: visible; --spectra-background-color: var(--ast-global-color-5);\" class=\"spectra-is-root-container alignfull spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow spectra-background-color wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"\t>\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-mgj4a61r-x1dhcn\" style=\"overflow: visible\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow wp-block-spectra-container spectra-hide-desktop spectra-hide-tablet spectra-hide-mobile\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n<div data-spectra-id=\"spectra-21fd9d93-8de9-4728-82a2-60772db10a9f\" style=\"overflow: visible\" class=\"spectra-overlay-color spectra-overflow wp-block-spectra-container\" data-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\n\n<figure data-spectra-id=\"spectra-gallery-img-207\" class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/lacupaethicalbrunch.com\/fine-dining-food\/\"><img l